headline: Senate passes stablecoin bill, a major victory for the crypto world
summary: The Senate on Tuesday passed a bill that would establish the first federal framework for dollar-backed cryptocurrencies known as stablecoins, a major victory for an industry that has pushed for more favorable oversight in Washington, D.C.

headline: Retail sales: What consumer data says about the middle class
summary: Deborah Weinswig, Coresight Research founder and CEO, joins Catalysts with Brad Smith and Academy Security head of macro strategy Peter Tchir to discuss the fresh retail sales data that was released Tuesday morning and how the numbers reflect consumer health. Weinswig also shares some promising retail names for investors to keep an eye on, like Amazon (AMZN) and Walmart (WMT).
